          "title": "SQL Queries",
          "expandable": true,
          "defaultExpansion": true,
          "helpText": "With Amazon Athena, you can pay based on the data scanned per query, or pay an hourly price for compute necessary to run your queries. You can get significant cost savings and performance gains by compressing, partitioning, or converting your data to a columnar format, because each of those operations reduces the amount of data that Athena needs to scan to or time needed to execute a query.",
